With our grassroots connections, we have been able to influence the <span style="color: #000000;">Center</span> delegates to support Joseph Joos as the new <span style="color: #000000;">Center</span> chairman. He has long been a friend of the <span style="color: #c00000;">**SPD**</span>, and will be more inclined to collaborate with us compared to Kaas. He also increases the appeal of the <span style="color: #000000;">Center Party</span> to the working class, though it comes at the cost of deepening the social and economic divisions once held together by religion.

